title: Happiness Abounds
body: If the world is so great, then we should all be very happy. As a matter of fact, I am very happy and many of us are in fact content with life. Don’t let the little things get you down. Life is awesome and happiness abounds

title: The wonders of love
body: Love is a unique bond between two people. Cherish it. When it comes your way, do not be short-sighted and let it go in favor of short-term thrills. Life is about balancing the long-run and the short-run and since love can potentially last a lifetime, make sure you do not let it go when it comes to you. That said, don’t manufacture love. If it’s not it, it’s not it. Painful though it may be in the moment, do not force things. Make your peace with the situation and move on.
